{"tid":507004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"METOO事件同以胸襲警件案有咩分別?","createTime":"2017-12-22T18:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T17:55:14.000Z","uid":12952,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e78e7bd7aeb0c483c9a0cd2b0b0b260335e1dfc","tid":507004,"uid":12952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T18:35:51.000Z","msg":"睇返姒胸襲警案嘅判詞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20160829/55569544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160829%2F55569544&d=Rq0KpPxW9tA6I4%2Fq6ambdV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=fb0d9222\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160829%2F55569544&h=fdc1d2a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20160829/55569544</a><br />\n法官在判詞中亦認為，無論是吳所指遭總督察陳嘉寶非禮，或是控方所指吳刻意用胸部撞向陳，繼而大叫「警察非禮」來誣陷對方，其實兩者均有其可能性，惟吳聲稱當時不知陳是警察，她被非禮後卻沒向在場警員求助，反而只顧找尋電話，有不合理之處。<br />\n<br />\n而metoo件事, 呂小姐嘅情況都係無論係教練真係有非禮佢 同呂小姐咁多年後想借METOO黎誣陷教練 都有可能 又冇證據證明<br />\n而疑點利益歸於被告 教練都係冇罪<br />\n<br />\n其實兩件事嘅思維係唔係一樣?"},{"pid":"93f0819d09ff535a0dab4a8af698f22d89e8b2d0","tid":507004,"uid":12952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T18:42:45.000Z","msg":"如果毗維一樣嘅話<br />\n即係話大部分人都係冇理性分析信曬傳媒既港豬<br />\n傳媒講緊咩就係支持"},{"pid":"75ef03f8ff8af7cd487cc682f03c27768f28fb3b","tid":507004,"uid":12952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T18:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果<span style=\"color: red;\">思</span>維一樣嘅話<br />\n即係話大部分人都係冇理性分析信曬傳媒既港豬<br />\n傳媒講緊咩就係支持</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6358c0f23145a087640549fb06697006c76867b0","tid":507004,"uid":12952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T18:47:33.000Z","msg":"仲要個時舊登好多人話以胸襲警判決可恥<br />\n今日又話反metoo<br />\n其實大家同女權人士都差唔多 邊一邊傷害到自己利益就撐邊一邊"},{"pid":"2ed0e13778fa9620744f43d43ca3124c9a3ccb90","tid":507004,"uid":12952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"